{
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"request vs job 的选择：\n- request: 一次性问答，如\"解释代码\"、\"生成正则\"\n- job: 复杂长期任务，需要多轮迭代自动执行，如\"重构整个模块\"\n"
,
"en"
:
"request vs job:\n- request: One-off Q&A, e.g. \"explain code\", \"generate regex\"\n- job: Complex long-term tasks with auto-iteration, e.g. \"refactor entire module\"\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"--file 可以多次使用附加多个文件，文件内容会注入到提示词中\n--output 将响应保存到文件，配合 --overwrite 可强制覆盖\n--json 要求 AI 以 JSON 格式输出，方便脚本解析\n"
,
"en"
:
"--file can be used multiple times to attach files (content injected into prompt)\n--output saves response to file, use with --overwrite to force replace\n--json requests structured JSON output for script parsing\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"--workspace 启用状态记忆，AI 可以在工作目录中创建/读取状态文件\n--reference-workspace 引用外部工作空间作为只读上下文，不修改外部目录\n"
,
"en"
:
"--workspace enables state memory; AI can create/read state files in working directory\n--reference-workspace references external workspace as read-only context\n"
}
]
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
"x agent request [options] <prompt>"
]
,
"--harness"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"指定 AI 工具（覆盖默认配置）"
,
"en"
:
"Specify AI tool (override default config)"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"$ref"
:
"x-advise://agent/data/harness.jso"
}
}
,
"-f|--file"
:
{
"#multiple"
:
true
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"附加文件到提示词（可多次使用）"
,
"en"
:
"Attach file to prompt (can be used multiple times)"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#exec"
:
"___x_cmd_advise__file"
}
}
,
"-o|--output"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"将 AI 响应保存到指定文件"
,
"en"
:
"Save AI response to specified file"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#exec"
:
"___x_cmd_advise__file"
}
}
,
"--overwrite"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"强制覆盖已存在的输出文件（需配合 --output）"
,
"en"
:
"Force overwrite existing output file (use with --output)"
}
}
,
"--debug"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"输出原始 JSON 和事件日志，用于排查问题"
,
"en"
:
"Output raw JSON and event logs for troubleshooting"
}
}
,
"--json"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"要求 AI 以 JSON 格式输出"
,
"en"
:
"Request JSON formatted output from AI"
}
}
,
"--pipe"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"从管道/标准输入读取内容附加到提示词"
,
"en"
:
"Read content from stdin/pipe to append to prompt"
}
}
,
"--stdout-file"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"捕获 AI 执行过程中的标准输出到文件"
,
"en"
:
"Capture AI execution stdout to file"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#exec"
:
"___x_cmd_advise__file"
}
}
,
"--stderr-file"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"捕获 AI 执行过程中的错误输出到文件"
,
"en"
:
"Capture AI execution stderr to file"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#exec"
:
"___x_cmd_advise__file"
}
}
,
"--timeout"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"请求超时时间（秒），0 表示不超时"
,
"en"
:
"Request timeout in seconds, 0 means no timeout"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"秒数（正整数）"
,
"en"
:
"Seconds (positive integer)"
}
}
}
,
"--session"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"复用已有会话 ID，保留对话历史"
,
"en"
:
"Reuse existing session ID to preserve conversation history"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"UUID 格式会话标识符"
,
"en"
:
"UUID format session identifier"
}
,
"#regex"
:
{
"^[0-9a-fA-F]{8}-[0-9a-fA-F]{4}-[0-9a-fA-F]{4}-[0-9a-fA-F]{4}-[0-9a-fA-F]{12}$"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"有效的 UUID 格式"
,
"en"
:
"Valid UUID format"
}
}
}
}
}
,
"--workspace"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"绑定工作目录，启用文件记忆和状态持久化"
,
"en"
:
"Bind working directory, enable file memory and state persistence"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#exec"
:
"___x_cmd_advise__dir"
}
}
,
"--no-workspace-session"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"绑定 workspace 但不自动复用 session，每次 request 都新建 session"
,
"en"
:
"Bind workspace without auto-reusing session; create a new session per request"
}
}
,
"--reference-workspace"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"引用外部工作空间作为只读上下文"
,
"en"
:
"Reference external workspace as read-only context"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#exec"
:
"___x_cmd_advise__dir"
}
}
,
"--no-thinking"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"跳过 AI 思考过程，直接输出结果（节省 token）"
,
"en"
:
"Skip AI thinking process, output result directly (save tokens)"
}
}
,
"#n"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"提示词内容，支持自然语言描述任务"
,
"en"
:
"Prompt content, supports natural language task description"
}
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent request \"Explain this code\""
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 单次问答——解释代码"
,
"en"
:
"Example: One-off Q&A — explain code"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent request --harness claude --file main.py \"Review and suggest improvements\""
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 指定 AI 工具 + 附加代码文件进行评审"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Specific AI tool + attach code file for review"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent request -f api.ts -f types.ts \"Generate API documentation\""
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 附加多个文件，生成 API 文档"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Attach multiple files to generate API docs"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent request --output result.md --overwrite \"Write a README\""
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 生成内容并保存到文件（强制覆盖）"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Generate content and save to file (force overwrite)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent request --json \"List all exported functions in this module\""
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 要求 JSON 格式输出，便于脚本解析"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Request JSON output for script parsing"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent request --workspace ./myproject \"Analyze codebase structure\""
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 绑定工作目录，AI 可以读写项目文件"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Bind working directory, AI can read/write project files"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent request --no-thinking \"Convert 2024-01-15 to Unix timestamp\""
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 简单转换任务，跳过思考节省 token"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Simple conversion, skip thinking to save tokens"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"echo \"Error log content\" | x agent request --pipe \"Analyze this error\""
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 管道输入 + AI 分析"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Pipe input + AI analysis"
}
]
}

